# Project Name

A Simple ERC20 dapp.


## Description

Simple dapp where you can mint and burn, approve the token

## Demo
live Demo :  https://bun-token-ercx.vercel.app/

Docs Demo : ( https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AvoyqRLv61QJqZJl1m76ZqmcPWWOfO4yK84DZJwaSIo/edit?usp=sharing )


### Prerequisites

- Next js
- Foundry
- Node.js
- npm

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   ```shell
   git clone https://github.com/binioosini/bunToken.git
   ```

2. Navigate to the project folder:

   ```shell
   cd bunToken
   ```

3. Install dependencies:
 
 ```shell
   cd ./simple
   ```

   ```shell
   npm install
   ```